EpiAwarePrototype.jl is a MODIFIED, DERIVED WORK based on that package.
Significant changes have been made, including (but not limited to):

  - The package has been renamed from `EpiAware` to `EpiAwarePrototype`, with a
    fresh package UUID.
  - The deep abstract type hierarchy and the per-concept model-generating
    functions (`generate_latent`, `generate_latent_infs`,
    `generate_observations`, `generate_epiaware`) have been re-architected
    around a single generic constructor, `as_turing_model`.
  - The package has been upgraded to build against the latest released
    Turing.jl and DynamicPPL.jl, replacing the removed `@submodel` macro with
    the `~ to_submodel(...)` form.
  - The components of the original package are ported and adapted to the new
    `as_turing_model` API. This is an early-stage prototype under active
    development.

